{"tid":752434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，5年前小弟係舊登開咗個POST，叫人入嚟留低想講嘅說話比五年後嘅自己","createTime":"2018-07-22T20:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T04:33:35.000Z","uid":33909,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"86dfdd2f04e1aabf1fb678d66927cb80c541b80b","tid":752434,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T20:15:54.000Z","msg":"雖然未齊齊整整夠五年，是鳩但啦<br />\n有印象睇過吓個post/有留過言嘅人入去睇下有冇自己份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好唔好彩我個AC比人bam咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年pm咗email比我嘅人真係唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有係post留過email比我嘅人我之後會send返條link比佢地<br />\n唔知多唔多人過咗嚟，不過希望佢地睇得返當年留比五年後嘅自己嘅說話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4802275&amp;&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4802275%26%26page%3D1&d=36Rt6SDeh3uDv2hevI%2BaV9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=bdd4bd6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4802275&amp;&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"dca35056807e4ef0a8d0eef283838aa1ef3eff15","tid":752434,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T20:23:10.000Z","msg":"有印象個post,但係搵唔到自己有留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04283f6aa65296cad618144bf94322a694af7683","tid":752434,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dca35056807e4ef0a8d0eef283838aa1ef3eff15","tid":752434,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T20:23:10.000Z","msg":"有印象個post,但係搵唔到自己有留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T20:24:32.000Z","msg":"自己咩名都唔記得？<im